-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Canexus Corp, Rogers Communications
-- 
-- Mon Oct 20, 2014 07:03AM EDT
-- None



Oct 20 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Canexus Corp and Rogers Communications, on Monday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Canexus Corp <CUS.TO>: CIBC raises to sector outperformer from sector performer * Rogers Communications <RCIb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to buy from hold  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Monday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Canexus Corp <CUS.TO>: CIBC raises to sector outperformer from sector performer * Fairfax Financial <FFH.TO>: CIBC raises target to C$450 from C$425; sector underperformer * Finning International <FTT.TO>: RBC cuts price target to C$35 from C$37; rating outperform * Intact Financial <IFC.TO>: CIBC raises target price to $84 from $76; sector outperformer * Paladin Energy Ltd <PDN.TO>: Dundee cuts price target to C$0.50 from C$0.60; rating buy * Rogers Communications <RCIb.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises to buy from hold * Rogers Communications <RCIb.TO>: NBF raises price target to C$46 from C$44.50 * Rogers Communications <RCIb.TO>: NBF raises to outperform from sector perform * Xtreme Drilling and Coil <XDC.TO>: Global Hunter Securities resumes with accumulate * Xtreme Drilling and Coil <XDC.TO>: Global Hunter Securities resumes with target C$3.70